Package org.workplicity.task

Classes in this package support NetPrevayle tasks.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
TaskListener A listener for NetTask errors.
 

Class Summary
DeleteTask This class sends a message to NetPrevayle to delete an entry in a repository.
ImportTask This class sends a message to NetPrevayle to import an entry into a repository.
InsertTask This class sends a message to NetPrevayle to insert an entry into a repository.
LoginTask This class sends a message to NetPrevayle to login to get a ticket needed for further tasks.
LogoutTask  
NetResult This class contains the results of a NetTask.
NetTask This class is an abstract NetPrevayle task.
NetTicket This class implements a ticket which is returned by NetPrevayle.
QueryTask This class sends a message to NetPrevayle to query a repository.
UpdateTask This class sends a message to NetPrevayle to update a repository.
 

Enum Summary
NetResult.Status Result status
